{"tid":2309244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被裁中國組助採：睇住TVB我就唔做有線啦！","createTime":"2020-12-02T11:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T11:55:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcd07634841a481a0066444bd93d4e3da5b894e","tid":2309244,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:55:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/R5GZFABMR5E7HFFKBLSUKVMMPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FR5GZFABMR5E7HFFKBLSUKVMMPI%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=574e6f61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FR5GZFABMR5E7HFFKBLSUKVMMPI%2F&h=10133753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/R5GZFABMR5E7HFFKBLSUKVMMPI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n有線裁員︱<br />\n爆許方輝指示跟無綫直播外交部記招 <br />\n被裁中國組助採：睇住TVB我就唔做有線啦！<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞部昨日（1日）大裁員，曾。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：有線新聞裁40人 不容新聞刺針 中國組總辭 5組主管辭職起義<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SY47SCOW0C_-p1CDfMn0pbGdWpI=/6375x3586/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L5O4I5GVMVDBNL5EWYVVDD75LU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSY47SCOW0C_-p1CDfMn0pbGdWpI%3D%2F6375x3586%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL5O4I5GVMVDBNL5EWYVVDD75LU.JPG&h=704a1ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃麗萍（中）在商台節目表示，裁員前公司與員工完全沒有溝通，批評不尊重新聞部運作。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1CrAoECKbLuwgChC62sS1e7m5zk=/6214x4143/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3SCWT3ZG4ZE5RAVIWV6JFECQGM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1CrAoECKbLuwgChC62sS1e7m5zk%3D%2F6214x4143%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3SCWT3ZG4ZE5RAVIWV6JFECQGM.JPG&h=dd8af08d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃麗萍直言，「最嬲係管理層完全無同我哋溝通......所有嘅風係出面傳返嚟」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n批管理層做法粗暴<br />\n<br />\n黃麗萍相信自己被裁是與管理層「新聞上有拗撬」，並指雖然早有心理準備，但到真正發生一刻仍感憤怒，「最嬲係管理層完全無同我哋溝通......所有嘅風係出面傳返嚟」。她認為，任何公司裁員都會與主管商量如何開源節流，「如果你真係咁重視員工資產」，但現在做法猶如「點指兵兵」，批評管理層做法「粗暴」，完全不尊重新聞部運作，令員工不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n黃麗萍亦質疑，管理層聲稱要重組資。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9ugcJqNjjpSPJ93Y8JhmYS8P_M4=/6672x3753/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K3PRNISM6NARBHDQNFWSN53LQM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9ugcJqNjjpSPJ93Y8JhmYS8P_M4%3D%2F6672x3753%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK3PRNISM6NARBHDQNFWSN53LQM.JPG&h=30b96125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有線新聞部昨日大裁員，港聞、中國、體育組，以至攝影師和剪片等不同崗位亦有員工被炒。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指許方輝曾提出可笑要求<br />\n<br />\n黃麗萍又提到有線新聞及公共事務副總經理、前TVB主播許方輝開會時曾提出「可笑要求」。她說，中國組曾提出做一個關於官派律師報道故仔，由當事人講述為何無權委託自己律師，但許則認為報道會有欠平衡，要求報道加入官派律師亦可幫到人的立場。而在港台《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲被捕當日，許竟未有打算將此新聞定作頭條，反認為以特首林鄭上京或檢測中心做頭條，「呢啲位同我哋距離太大&hellip;&hellip;唔知係真無知定有order在身」。她又透露，許曾質疑中國組沒有派員到外交部記者會，亦曾指無綫新聞有直播，為何有線沒有，黃直言「我睇住TVB做我就唔做有線啦！」並反駁「死跟住人哋唔會有自己特色」。<br />\n<br />\n對於是次裁員是否屬政治目的，黃麗萍坦言完全有可能，「唔係政治審查無人信」。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》英文版免費試睇：了解更多<br />\n<br />\n英文版已登錄《蘋果》App，立即下載/ 更新：iOS / Android<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n支持蘋果深度報道，深入社區，踢爆權貴，即Like蘋果專題及調查組FB專頁！"},{"pid":"1fe5429fd71bf6d2d0aa6e55d23ba347010e27c6","tid":2309244,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:55:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}